# @{{name}}/eslint-config

Internal ESLint configuration package for the monorepo.

## Usage

This package re-exports configurations from `@morphdsl/eslint-config`. Individual packages use it via their `eslint.config.ts`:

```typescript
import { configs } from "@{{name}}/eslint-config";

export default configs.generated;
```

## Available Configs

- `configs.generated` - Standard config for generated code
- `configs.cli` - Additional rules for CLI entry points
